es.upm.dit.dscc.DHT

Class TableManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • es.upm.dit.dscc.DHT.TableManager

  • public class TableManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    aalonso This class manages the tables in a DHT. It includes the information required for the server/process that provides the tables in the DHT.
